      <title>黄金持续下跌，因交易员权衡美国数据和利率前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/gold-xauusd-holds-slump-as-traders-weigh-mixed-us-data-rate-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国数据好坏参半，交易员纷纷在美国联邦储备委员会 (FED/美联储) 今年最后一次政策会议前获利了结，黄金价格维持下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/gold-xauusd-holds-slump-as-traders-weigh-mixed-us-data-rate-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 00:55:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制裁前景抵消供应过剩影响，油价有望周线上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国可能对伊朗和俄罗斯实施更严厉的制裁，抵消了人们对明年全球石油供应大幅过剩的持续担忧，油价每周均上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
